TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"You've got more and more kayakers, windsurfers and surfers competing with more 
and more sharks in Southern California. It's just a matter of time before the 
sharks and the people meet." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Ralph Collier, president of the Shark Research Committee, a Los Angeles 
scientific organization. 
</P>
