JAPAN -- FOREIGN POLICY; BUSH, GEORGE; TAKESHITA, NOBORU; JAPAN -- FOREIGN AID; 
JAPAN -- GOVERNMENT; JAPAN -- DEFENSE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
