NICARAGUA -- REVOLTS; HONDURAS -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- NICARAGUA; AZCONA HOYO, 
JOSE; QUAYLE, DAN; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- NICARAGUA; GUERRILLAS 
-- HONDURAS 
</P>
