EL SALVADOR; EL SALVADOR -- REVOLTS; FARABUNDO MARTI NATIONAL LIBERATION FRONT 
(EL SALVADOR); CENTRAL AMERICAN PEACE; EL SALVADOR -- ARMED FORCES; EL SALVADOR 
-- ELECTIONS 
</P>
