RELATIONS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; PRISON ASSAULTS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; CROSS 
BURNING; POLICE MISCONDUCT; POLICE BRUTALITY; GANGS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY 
