A persistent drizzle Friday afternoon caused postponement of the second round 
of qualifying for the Chief Auto Parts Winternationals drag race at Pomona. 
</P>
<P>
Weather permitting, qualifying for the National Hot Rod Assn. event will resume 
today at the Fairgrounds strip with pro classes running at 11 a.m. and 3 p.m. 
If today's program is washed out, however, the entire schedule will not be 
resumed until next Friday. 
</P>
