his showcase home. ; Photo, COLOR, A window view at San Juan's Decorative Arts 
Center. ; Photo, COLOR, The atrium area used for dining at Durenberger's 
Capistrano Beach home. ; Photo, This 18th-Century English formal room is 
featured at the Center for the Study of Decorative Arts. GARY AMBROSE / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
